<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Novasphere Pricing</title>
    <style>
        /* General Page Styles */
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .pricing-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .header-section {
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .header-section h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #222;
        }

        .header-section p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* Pricing Cards Layout */
        .pricing-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: stretch;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            width: 300px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        /* Special Styling for the Middle Card (Pro) */
        .card.popular {
            border: 2px solid #2546bc;
            position: relative;
        }

        .badge-popular {
            position: absolute;
            top: -15px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background-color: #2546bc;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Typography inside cards */
        .tier-name {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .price-main {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #222;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .price-sub {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #888;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #eee;
            margin: 30px 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Features List */
        .features-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: left;
            flex-grow: 1; /* Pushes content to fill space */
        }

        .features-list li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #444;
            display: flex;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .checkmark {
            color: #2546bc;
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .green-check {
            color: #28a745;
        }

        /* Footer CTA */
        .cta-footer {
            margin-top: 60px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #eef2ff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .cta-text {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #2546bc;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .pricing-grid {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .card {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 350px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="pricing-container">
    
    <div class="header-section">
        <h1>Flexible Deployment</h1>
        <p>From small contractors to government enterprises.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-grid">
        
        <div class="card">
            <div class="tier-name">Basic</div>
            <div class="price-main">$0<span class="price-sub">/mo</span></div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>

            <ul class="features-list">
                <li><span class="checkmark">✓</span> Up to 10 Users</li>
                <li><span class="checkmark">✓</span> Max 5 Projects</li>
                <li><span class="checkmark">✓</span> Supplier Comparison</li>
                <li><span class="checkmark">✓</span> Material Tracking</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card popular">
            <div class="badge-popular">MOST POPULAR</div>
            <div class="tier-name" style="color: #2546bc; font-weight:bold;">Pro & Pro+</div>
            <div class="price-main" style="font-size: 2rem;">Subscription</div>
            <div class="price-sub">Cloud SaaS Model</div>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <ul class="features-list">
                <li><span class="checkmark green-check">✓</span> <strong>Unlimited</strong> Users & Projects</li>
                <li><span class="checkmark green-check">✓</span> Basic Progress Reports</li>
                <li><span class="checkmark green-check">✓</span> <strong>Pre-Delay Alerts</strong></li>
                <li><span class="checkmark green-check">✓</span> Priority Support</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="tier-name">Enterprise</div>
            <div class="price-main" style="font-size: 2rem;">On-Prem</div>
            <div class="price-sub">Private Server Deployment</div>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <ul class="features-list">
                <li><span class="checkmark">✓</span> Full Data Control</li>
                <li><span class="checkmark">✓</span> Custom Integrations (ERP/BIM)</li>
                <li><span class="checkmark">✓</span> Government Compliance</li>
                <li><span class="checkmark">✓</span> Dedicated Account Manager</li>
                <li><span class="checkmark">✓</span> SLA-backed Support</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="cta-footer">
        <span class="cta-text">Interest in our product? Contact customer support to start with Novasphere.</span>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>